   "source": [
    "### Question 11 \u2014 Which country has the most wins historically?\n",
    "\n",
    "A team wins when they are the **home team** with a Home Win result, **or** the **away team** with an Away Win result.  \n",
    "We extract both sets of winners, combine them, and count total wins per nation."
   ]
